    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >主要特色：</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>- 情感故事</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >体验一个关于爱、牺牲和不懈追求幸福的温馨故事。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>- 惊艳视觉</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >动画CG和女主角的立绘将凯恩和尼卡的世界栩栩如生地呈现出来。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>- 沉浸式原声带</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >让音乐带你深入这个永恒寒冬的旅程。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3000310/extras/4bf71df09c5ef1c4107c0832b5ff337e.poster.avif?t=1731603256\" width=616 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3000310/extras/4bf71df09c5ef1c4107c0832b5ff337e.webm?t=1731603256\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3000310/extras/4bf71df09c5ef1c4107c0832b5ff337e.mp4?t=1731603256\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>故事</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在这个寒冷、残酷的世界里，只有妹妹尼卡的爱让凯恩活了下来。每天，他在垃圾堆中寻找任何有价值的东西来养活他们。但凯恩的努力没有成功——他们的处境只会越来越糟。绝望中，他向两兄弟因维和阿瓦里借了一笔钱。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >然而，债务的重担太过沉重。无论凯恩多么努力地赚钱——他一次次失败。还款日到了，但凯恩无法还钱。所以……因维和阿瓦里决定带走尼卡，让她成为奴隶。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >绝望而心碎的凯恩向天祈求改变命运的力量。但神明保持沉默，他的祈祷没有得到回应。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >“没有人会救尼卡。没有人……除了我。”</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3000310/extras/42e9fd1beafe44031964fe9a3b33e1ce.poster.avif?t=1731603256\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3000310/extras/42e9fd1beafe44031964fe9a3b33e1ce.webm?t=1731603256\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3000310/extras/42e9fd1beafe44031964fe9a3b33e1ce.mp4?t=1731603256\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《凯恩 × 尼卡》是一部关于绝望世界中持久之爱与决心的视觉小说。这个感人的故事通过动画CG、生动的角色设计和令人难忘的原声带栩栩如生地呈现出来。沉浸在这个绝望的故事中，看看凯恩的爱能否战胜命运。他能赢吗？还是……</p>",
